{"tid":2007060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：對跪地市民向天開第一槍既警員梁子聰獲指揮官嘉獎","createTime":"2020-05-08T07:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T03:21:08.000Z","uid":22556,"like":84,"dislike":485,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0a458ced9a8c638c2f390745d57ac30a22e2da","tid":2007060,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:20:09.000Z","msg":"網上流傳一份警隊人事通告，18名曾鎮壓反修例示威的警員獲得「指揮官嘉獎」。其中，去年8月25日在荃灣二陂坊，於一名下跪市民面前向天鳴槍的高級警長梁子聰獲嘉獎；另有2名警長、1名高級警員及5名警員，被指在8月25日荃灣鎮壓中有「英勇表現」並受傷，同樣獲得指揮官嘉獎，即因為8.25荃灣鎮壓獲嘉獎的警員共計有9人。《蘋果》查證後證實嘉獎名單真確。梁子聰是在反修例示威中首名使用實彈的警員。<br />\n<br />\n詳情 :<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200508&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60916687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200508%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60916687&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=9578b62e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200508%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60916687&h=069cc487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200508&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60916687</a>"},{"pid":"d99ddf6d507bcaf1f7c912dad57127fbed535cbc","tid":2007060,"uid":184261,"like":135,"dislike":3,"score":132,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"軍政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7d2494a35fb96b3928247cbf7e8a678b170b18","tid":2007060,"uid":41292,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:21:22.000Z","msg":"快啲返比多啲獎喇<br />\n<br />\n30000 thx"},{"pid":"1799a238fa7d5dbad8e8bd66e03b4008868b2a6b","tid":2007060,"uid":8014,"like":91,"dislike":3,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"殺人放火金腰帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm